                \n </database_json_schema>
                \n Popola lo schema con i dati del seguente requirement e ritorna il JSON risultante.
                \n <sr_json>
                \n {"id":"CR 1.9C","fr":"FR_1","software_application":true,"host_device":true,"embedded_device":true,"network_device":true,"source":"IEC 62443-4-2: CR 1.9(c)","description":"For components that utilize public-key-based authentication, those components shall provide directly or integrate into a system that provides the capability within the same IACS environment to validate certificates by checking a given certificate’s revocation status.","reference":"Strength of public key-based authentication - check certificate's revocation status","capability_sl":"2, 3, 4"}
                \n </sr_json>
                \n Ritorna il JSON risultante.
